  &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;alg.cubing.net&#x2F;?type=alg&amp;view=playback&amp;alg=(R_U_R-_U-)_(R-_F)_(R2_U-)_(R-_U-_R_U)_(R-_F-)&amp;puzzle=2x2x2&amp;setup=F_R_U-_R-_U_R_U_R2_F-_R_U_R_U-_R-&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(R U R&#x27; U&#x27;) (R&#x27; F) (R2 U&#x27;) (R&#x27; U&#x27; R U) (R&#x27; F&#x27;)&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
